question: Tī-sī ū ki-liâm hō͘-chua̍h chū-tē ē tit-tio̍h GT3 liân-sai ê koan-hē? Chòe tsu-liệu ê ki-pún lâi kái-sek.
answer: Chū-tē ē tit-tio̍h koan-hē kap GT3 liân-sai ê koan-hē sī chiok jı̍t. Tī 14 pái ê lúi, hō͘-chua̍h chū-tē ē tit-tio̍h GT3 liân-sai ê tūi-iúⁿ kan-tāⁿ ū 3 pái: tē 5 pái ê 'No. 1 Barwell Motorsport', tē 6 pái ê 'No. 6 Team RPM', kap tē 12 pái ê 'No. 23 Christians in Motorsport'. Che chiàm 21.4% ê iâⁿ-lu̍t, jīn-uî tī chia ê liân-sai-kùi, hō͘-chua̍h chū-tē bōe siâⁿ siâⁿ hō͘ GT3 lâi-iúⁿ ê tōa lì-ek.

question: Koh-iáⁿ ê siōng-tn̂g ê pí-sài tiong, koh-iáⁿ ê chhia-chúi thûi-chhia-chá ê si̍t-choâⁿ ê kiat-kó sī siáng?
Donington Park kap Brands Hatch ê só͘-chāi sûn-khoân, lóng-chóng ê pí-sài sî-kan sī kúi-bái hun-zhōng?
Chiah-sī tī-sī bô tiâu-tāi 4 go̍eh ia̍h-sī 9 go̍eh kí-hêng ê pí-sài ê GT3 tiâⁿ-ka kiàⁿ-tūi?
Koh-choán gûi-chiá ê liân-bó-chok, GT3 kap GTC nn̄g ê lūi cheng-chiàn, ū nn̄g ê choán-chhiú chūi-chí siōng chē sèng-lī?
Koa-chū iân-tsāi ê sî-kan, teh-beh kā "99 Hō Beechdean Motorsport" tī GTC khu ê sîng-tsi̍k tsuán-uán sió-liám liáu-kái.
answer: "99 Hō Beechdean Motorsport" ê sîng-tsi̍k sī tshut-sì tēⁿ-tio̍h chin hó, āu-piah kiat-sū mā chin phah-peh, sīu-tāi tiong-kan ū tsi̍t duāi tsuáⁿ sî-kan tsióng-siòng chin kīn. In tī 4 goe̍h (tē 3 kap tē 4 luán) tī Donington Park tit-tio̍h liân-sio̍k chuán, āu-lâi kàu 8 goe̍h bo̍e-chhoē (tē 10 luán) tī Thruxton chiah koh tit-chuán. In tī 9 goe̍h bo̍e-chhoē (tē 13 kap tē 14 luán) tī Rockingham tsiânn-tsò tsiânn-pài, tshut-hiān liân-sio̍k chuán, tì-tsò in chiū-sī GTC khu lāi siōng sîng-kong ê tūi chi̍t ê, m̄-koh tsuán-uán ê sî-kan ê sîng-tsi̍k bô tiāⁿ.

question: Pai tiam 'Barwell Motorsport' (chha̍p-sîm No. 1, No. 2, kap No. 3) tit-tio̍h ê GT3 hāng-ba̍k tit-cheng ê phah-sàng tiâu-tîm ū sì-chē phah-sàng?
Lioh-choân liap-chi̍p ê liap-sài sî-kan, ū nn̄g-ê kiat-kip ê liap-sài sî-kan ke̍k-tōa hām kî-thaⁿ sió-khíⁿ bô-kāng?
